                                        (<dimensions>
                                            <width>2.15</width>
                                            <height>0.435</height>
                                            <depth>0.61</depth>
                                        </dimensions>).</p>
                                </support>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in four columns of two lines each and one more line on the full width; in each column, the space between letters
                                    fluctuates so that both lines have the same length; the four columns are not equally dispatched on the width of the face, 
                                    but correspond to the placement of the statues, whereas line 9 stretches at equal distance of both ends</layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
