                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, p. <citedRange>103</citedRange> (prosopography, date), , p. <citedRange>368</citedRange>, number 93 (text)</bibl>. 
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#ensoli2010"/>, p. <citedRange>132</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
